<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-12-17T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-12-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="351" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d351">
                    <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Baker</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi></head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">La
                                Libertad</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-12-17"><hi rend="italic">December 17,
                            1894</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                    <p>Mosquito Indians have surrendered their rights under the treaty of 1860 and
                        been incorporated with Nicaragua.</p>
